name: NVJOBMagicCircle v1.0. For generating magic summoning circle
description:
For developers only.

NVJOBMagicCircle v1.0. This is a model for generating magic summoning circle assets.

This is a model of generating magic summoning circle images (for video games and more). It is trained on a large dataset of summoning magic circle images, allowing her to create new unique summoning magic circles based on the training data.

Game developers can use this model to create their own magic summoning circle, allowing them to create unique visuals in their games.

With this model, developers can save time and effort that would otherwise be spent manually creating each magic summoning circle.

Stable Diffusion Parameters:

Sampling method - Euler a

Sampling steps - 30-80

Resolution - 768x768

CFG Scale - 4-12

Or

Sampling method - DPM++ 2M Karras

Sampling steps - 23-28

Resolution - 768x768

CFG Scale - 7-10

For higher resolution use Hires. fix or upscale.

• nvjobmagiccircle magic summoning circle, various symbols, pentagramus, white background, intricate

• nvjobmagiccircle magic summoning circle, sun, moon, hieroglyphs, symbols, white background, black and white

• nvjobmagiccircle magic dragon summoning circle, inscriptions, symbols, white background, black and white

• nvjobmagiccircle magic summoning circle, demonic, infernal portal, inscriptions, symbols, white background, black and white, simple, symmetrically

• nvjobmagiccircle magic summoning circle, a circle with many different symbols in it, including the names of all the zodiac signs and the numbers of all the stars, magic circle, summoning circle, black magic circle on white background, on a white background, black and white, abstract sacred geometry, complicated, with symbols, inscriptions, signatures
